Good morning everyone... Would love to get my mind off the sadness 😌 Can we all discuss Episode 2... What were your thoughts?? 👁 ALOT happened w @shanedawson and so many truths revealed. Who’s ready for episode 3 already?? PS. It’s ok to have moments of hopelessness and doubt. That’s normal and don’t let anyone else tell you otherwise 💯 But you can’t let those thoughts consume you, you have to push forward no matter how hard it is.

I love the month of October and all of the #Halloween makeup looks everywhere 🖤 Creating art and playing with cosmetics is the only thing keeping me sane right now. The iconic #BlueBlood palette is perfect for the spooky season 🧟‍♂️ #jeffreestarcosmetics photo by: @vivian.elizabethh

#RIPDaddyStar 💔 With heavy hearts we have to share the devastating news that our dog Daddy passed away early this morning. His body couldn’t handle the surgery plus the complications of his medical condition. I can’t put into words how much we love our pets and how much this hurts. Daddy meant the world to us and was such a light in our home. Every day was smiles and he brought so much love into our lives..😌 Nathan and I know that Daddy and Diamond are together watching over us. My heart breaks in a million pieces thinking about not snuggling with him tonight. We love you big man 🐶
